Package oogasalad.editor.controller

Class EditorEventHandler

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.controller.EditorEventHandler
public class EditorEventHandler extends Object
Handles editing of events, conditions, and outcomes associated with editor objects. Provides methods for adding, removing, modifying, and retrieving event-related data.
